 armored. As a result, it can eat grass and berries without having to fight."},{"version":"white","text":"It is outstandingly armored. As a result, it can eat grass and berries without having to fight."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It is outstandingly armored. As a result, it can eat grass and berries without having to fight."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It is outstandingly armored. As a result, it can eat grass and berries without having to fight."},{"version":"x","text":"It habitually polishes its face by rubbing it against tree trunks. It is weak to attacks from behind."},{"version":"y","text":"It was generated from a fossil dug out of a layer of clay that was older than anyone knows. It has a sturdy face."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"It habitually polishes its face by rubbing it against tree trunks. It is weak to attacks from behind."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"It was generated from a fossil dug out of a layer of clay that was older than anyone knows. It has a sturdy face."},{"version":"sun","text":"Many fossils of this Pok\u00e9mon have been found, but almost none have shown signs of damage to the face."},{"version":"moon","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon lived in primeval jungles. Few enemies would have been willing to square off against its heavily armored face, so it\u2019s thought."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"A mild-mannered, herbivorous Pok\u00e9mon, it used its face to dig up tree roots to eat. The skin on its face was plenty tough."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Although its fossils can be found in layers of primeval rock, nothing but its face has ever been discovered."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Much remains unknown about this Pok\u00e9mon, as few have ever seen it. However, we know that it is calm and dislikes conflict, and it enjoys polishing its face against trees and rocks."}],"evo":{"name":"shieldon","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location